hs|nh|hs|sh|nt|There was no way that I was going to avoid a heart loser against these guys so I claimed my contract with an overtrick for +130. The real purpose of this ^*BDeal of the Week^*N was to introduce the ^*BReverse Flannery Responses^*N convention, but I hope you enjoyed reading about the play of this deal as well! |mc|10|
